title: Sony Xperia Z5 arrives in the UK
text:
Sony Xperia Z5 arrives in the UK 
Published By: AndroidAuthority.com - Today 
The Sony Xperia Z5 is now available to purchase in the UK through retailer Carphone Warehouse. Other shops should stock the phone next week....
